## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture the full scope of the FLCCC's activities or the latest developments. The credibility assessment is limited to the information retrieved and may not reflect the organization's current standing or future actions. Additionally, the dynamic nature of scientific research means that new evidence could emerge, potentially altering the conclusions drawn here.